{"tid":148601,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇頹歌？","createTime":"2017-03-08T16:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T12:59:39.000Z","uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dfdb1fc1e0915fcea8106a7e51718404da1c202","tid":148601,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅頹歌 我覺得係啲歌詞同旋律都沉重 <br />\n聽完會好撚頹 <br />\n雖然會愈聽愈頹 但真心好撚正<br />\n毒撚格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n林宥嘉 陳小春唔洗講啦 <br />\n兵歌首選 <br />\n啲人成日以為兵歌得周柏豪 其實老實講首首啲旋律好似一尻樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麥浚龍又另一境界 暗黑變態<br />\n好撚正<br />\n近期大愛李榮浩 佢啲歌又係頹頹地兵歌feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de72fdd62971d2f1e47a19fcf3db6773698db155","tid":148601,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"李榮浩 𣎴將就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9d912b4b3cadcbd283572374d7eee57d60a439","tid":148601,"uid":37961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"李榮浩個演唱會幾正😎✋🏻"},{"pid":"c4f88d3b0ed9a2ad90ac0e61209a3b311ca50cee","tid":148601,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"黃秋生-幸福摩天輪"},{"pid":"79c17b80056fff38dd617dce3e6b42e9d23e19d4","tid":148601,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"Taking back sunday - your own disaster<br />\n<br />\n屌打晒你D咩廣東sad歌個曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139595d9ebc539649ee26c785ebb6bb3fca328b7","tid":148601,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"反感，煽情，又唔好聽，洗唔洗日都世界末日啊?最憎成堆咁既歌，聽到腦爆。"},{"pid":"966